      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄭風·020.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">野有蔓草.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>野有蔓草，零露漙兮。有美一人，清揚婉兮。邂逅相遇，適我願兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the moor is the creeping grass,
And how heavily is it loaded with dew !
There was a beautiful man,
Lovely, with clear eyes and fine forehead !
We met together accidentally,
And so my desire was satisfied.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
