      <prop type="x-translation-ref">野有蔓草.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>野有蔓草，零露瀼瀼。有美一人，婉如清揚。邂逅相遇，與子偕臧。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the moor is the creeping grass,
Heavily covered with dew.
There was a beautiful man,
Lovely, with clear eyes and fine forehead !
We met together accidentally,
And he and I were happy together.</seg>
      </tuv>
